content.rendered:
Directed By Sai Kabir

Written By Sai Kabir

Stars Nawazuddin Siddiqui (Guest Appearance). Sanjay Mishra (Salim). Tigmanshu Dhulia (Shamshuddin). Tanya Lal (Alka). Sadiya Siddiqui (Safiya). Aaliya Siddiqui (Masoom). Mukesh S. Bhatt (Rambo (as Mukesh Bhatt)). Praful Rathod (DANISH). Rahul Mittra (Wasim). Hemendra Dandotiya (Matu Yadav). Deepak Soni (RINKU). Mayank Kaul (KEDAR). Himanshu Pandey (Sonu). Mukesh Kumar Bhatt . Prashant Chodhri (Ghanshyam). Anoop Gautam (NITU). Lalit Singh Pokhariya (ZAFAR). Prakash Ramchandani (GUARD AT THE GATE). Neeraj Vyas (HARI SINGH). Dhiraj Kumawat (SALIM’S SON). Raj Sharma (SAEED BHOPALI). Bishna Chouhan (MRS. MISHRA (PRAMOD’S MOTHER)). Farooque (QURESHI). Rahul Mitra (WASIM BAIG). Himanshu (SONU). Maya Band (ALKA). Manoj Mishra (MUJAHID). Lb Yadav (PURSHOTTAM BABU). Prashant (GHANSHYAM). Satendra Soni (PRAMOD).

Language Hindi

Producer Aaliya Siddiqui. Baljinder Khanna. Seema Narula. Muazzam Beg. Ashutosh Bhargav.

Production The Filmy Zilla. Y S Entertainment
